sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Maintainer as Project Maintainer
    participant Repo as Git Repository
    participant Shell as Local Shell
    participant UV as uv Tooling
    participant BuilderPy as src/build.py
    participant Latex as pdflatex
    participant GH as GitHub Repository
    participant Actions as GitHub Actions Workflow
    participant Docker as Docker Build/Run in CI
    participant Pages as GitHub Pages

    Maintainer->>Repo: Clone/pull repository
    Maintainer->>Shell: Enter project directory
    Shell->>Shell: Read .python-version (3.12)
    Shell->>UV: uv sync
    alt Dependency sync succeeds
        UV-->>Shell: Environment ready
    else Dependency sync fails
        UV-->>Maintainer: Install/configuration error output
    end

    loop Feature/content iteration
        Maintainer->>Shell: Edit src/data.yaml and/or src/template.tex
        opt Build logic change
            Maintainer->>Shell: Edit src/build.py
        end
        opt Optional linting
            Maintainer->>UV: uv run ruff check .
        end
        Maintainer->>UV: uv run src/build.py
        BuilderPy->>Latex: Compile generated.tex to PDF
        alt Local build succeeds
            UV-->>Maintainer: resume.pdf updated in project root
        else Local build fails
            UV-->>Maintainer: Validation/LaTeX error logs
            Maintainer->>Shell: Fix YAML/template/build logic and retry
        end
    end

    Maintainer->>GH: Push commit to main
    GH->>Actions: Trigger build-deploy workflow (push)
    Note over GH,Actions: Manual trigger is also available via workflow_dispatch.
    Actions->>Docker: Build cached CI image from Dockerfile
    Actions->>Docker: Run containerized command (uv sync --frozen && uv run src/build.py)
    alt CI build and deploy succeed
        Actions->>Pages: Publish _site/index.html + resume.pdf
        Pages-->>Maintainer: Updated public URL available
    else CI fails
        Actions-->>Maintainer: Failed run with step logs
        Maintainer->>Actions: Open logs, identify failing step, patch code/config, push again
    end

    opt Environment and configuration maintenance
        Maintainer->>Shell: Update pyproject.toml/uv.lock dependencies
        Maintainer->>Shell: Update Dockerfile TeX/Python runtime when needed
        Maintainer->>Shell: Update .github/workflows/build-deploy.yml pipeline behavior
    end

    Note over Maintainer,Repo: Database migrations are not part of this codebase (no DB layer implemented).
    Note over Maintainer,Repo: No dedicated automated test suite is currently present in repository files.
    Note over Maintainer,Actions: Monitoring/debugging is primarily GitHub Actions logs + run status.
    Note over Maintainer,GH: Formal release/tag automation is not implemented in current workflow.
